        },
        "text_GjLMYb": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Our founder's journey began in Seoul, where she discovered the transformative power of Korean skincare philosophy. The focus on gentle, consistent care and innovative ingredients changed her relationship with her skin forever.<br/>Returning to San Diego, she noticed the overwhelming nature of the K-beauty market. Too many options, confusing routines, and unclear ingredient lists left people frustrated rather than excited about skincare.<br/>Seoul Glow Lab was born to solve this problem – curating only the best, most effective products while providing the education needed to use them successfully.</p>",
