        "ai_gen_block_d8b523e_rNb8iR": {
          "type": "ai_gen_block_d8b523e",
          "name": "Single Events",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "image_desktop": "shopify://shop_images/flyerv3.jpg",
            "image_mobile": "shopify://shop_images/flyerv3.jpg",
            "image_border_radius": 4,
            "title": "House of B x Seoul Glow Lab | Wrap & Reset: The Winter Film Ritual",
            "description": "<p>Stepping into winter with intention—softening into slower evenings, colder air, and the quiet invitation to restore what feels depleted. As the season asks us to turn inward, we’re gathering for a ritual that wraps the skin in care and resets the nervous system, so you can move through the darkest months with clarity, calm, and a silver-soft glow.<br/><br/>Join us for wrap & reset: the winter film ritual, a co-created experience with House of B featuring their Glow Glutathione Face Film, an ingredient-forward spotlight on water as the foundation of hydrogel technology, and a <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sacredsoundhaven?igsh=NTc4MTIwNjQ2YQ==\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.instagram.com/sacredsoundhaven?igsh=NTc4MTIwNjQ2YQ==\"><strong>guided sound bath, by Cora,</strong></a> to deepen rest and release.<br/><br/>We’ll move through a curated flow: settling in with a welcome mocktail and ingredient bar, applying the face film step-by-step with our Glow Advisors, resting into a winter-inspired sound journey, and closing with a collective peel + confetti glow reveal on the stairs.<br/><br/>Each guest will receive a curated goodie bag to extend the ritual at home.<br/><br/>To help set the atmosphere, we invite guests to come dressed comfortably in white, silver, or grey. It’s not required, but strongly encouraged—these tones create a soft, cohesive winter palette that elevates the experience for everyone.<br/><br/>Come as you are. Bare skin encouraged for the face film ritual; we’ll take care of the rest.</p>",
            "event_date": "Monday, December 15, 2025",
            "event_time": "7:00 PM – 8:30 PM PST",
            "location": "𝘀𝗲𝗼𝘂𝗹 𝗴𝗹𝗼𝘄 𝗹𝗮𝗯 | 4344 convoy street, suite C-2",
