            "image_border_radius": 4,
            "title": "Winter Rituals: Gentle Movement + Gua Sha Flow",
            "description": "<p>🎟️ $𝟱𝟱 𝗥𝗦𝗩𝗣 𝗧𝗜𝗖𝗞𝗘𝗧 | 12 spots<br/>✔️welcome tea + 45 min. of gentle movement & sound healing guided by @<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/withkateco/\" title=\"https://www.instagram.com/withkateco/\">withkateco</a><br/>✔️45 min. gua sha workshop led by @<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sabrinahkim\" title=\"https://www.instagram.com/sabrinahkim\">soulcarestandard</a><br/>✔️complimentary @<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/apoterra/\" title=\"https://www.instagram.com/apoterra/\">apoterra </a>skincare kit to take the ritual home<br/>✔️after-hours access to @<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/seoulglowlab/?hl=en\" title=\"https://www.instagram.com/seoulglowlab/?hl=en\">seoulglowlab </a>with a 15% off shopping discount</p>",
            "event_date": "Monday, December 1, 2025",
            "event_time": "7:00 PM - 9:00 PM PST",
            "location": "𝘀𝗲𝗼𝘂𝗹 𝗴𝗹𝗼𝘄 𝗹𝗮𝗯 | 4344 convoy street, suite C-2",
            "hosted_by": "kate + co & Sabrina Kim",
            "price": "$55.00",
            "long_description": "<p>Stepping into December with intention–as we emerge from the new moon in Scorpio's deep reflection & move through mercury’s introspective retrograde through the same waters, we’re gathering for a moment of stillness, ritual & reset. a return to ourselves, a soft alignment with the collective, & a gentle shedding of what no longer serves us.<br/><br/>join @<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/withkateco/\" title=\"https://www.instagram.com/withkateco/\">withkateco </a>& @<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sabrinahkim\" title=\"https://www.instagram.com/sabrinahkim\">soulcarestandard </a>for an evening of gentle movement, meditative soundbath, & a guided gua sha flow at @seoulglowlab, San Diego's newest k-beauty space. a soft pause amidst the holiday season—a chance to tune inward, to honor who we’ve been becoming in 2025 & to feel into what we’re carrying forward into 2026.<br/><br/>come as you are. mats & warm lavender towels provided—bare skin encouraged.</p>",
            "button_text": "𝗥𝗦𝗩𝗣 𝗧𝗜𝗖𝗞𝗘𝗧 | 12 spots",
